
Comments

(Post Request)
comments/:account_id/project/:project_id/section/:section/:section_object_id
-Creates New Calendar
    Get Params
        account_id
        project_id
        section
        section_object_id
    Post Params
        content
        subscribers ( javascript array, like -> [4744618, 3744548] )
        attachments ( javascript object, like -> [{"token": "", "name": "final_mockup.png"}] )

(Delete Request)
comments/:account_id/project/:project_id/comment/:comment_id
-Deletes A Comment
    Get Params
        account_id
        project_id
        comment_id